21}, {\"ngram\": \"the scores\", \"from\": 17128, \"to\": 17138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gymnast with the highest cumulative score wins the gold.\", \"from\": 17169, \"to\": 17229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The gymnast\", \"from\": 17169, \"to\": 17180}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest cumulative score\", \"from\": 17186, \"to\": 17214}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 17220, \"to\": 17228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In each of the four events, gymnasts are judged on their execution and level of difficulty by a panel of nine total judges.Learn more here.\", \"from\": 17231, \"to\": 17370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the four events\", \"from\": 17242, \"to\": 17257}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 17259, \"to\": 17267}, {\"ngram\": \"their execution\", \"from\": 17282, \"to\": 17297}, {\"ngram\": \"level\", \"from\": 17302, \"to\": 17307}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulty\", \"from\": 17311, \"to\": 17321}, {\"ngram\": \"a panel\", \"from\": 17325, \"to\": 17332}, {\"ngram\": \"nine total judges\", \"from\": 17336, \"to\": 17353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today's action in the all-around final will put the world's top gymnasts to the test across four events: vault, uneven bars, balance beam and floor exercise.\", \"from\": 17372, \"to\": 17529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Today's action\", \"from\": 17372, \"to\": 17386}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around final\", \"from\": 17390, \"to\": 17410}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's top gymnasts\", \"from\": 17420, \"to\": 17444}, {\"ngram\": \"the test\", \"from\": 17448, \"to\": 17456}, {\"ngram\": \"four events\", \"from\": 17464, \"to\": 17475}, {\"ngram\": \"uneven bars\", \"from\": 17484, \"to\": 17495}, {\"ngram\": \"balance beam\", \"from\": 17497, \"to\": 17509}, {\"ngram\": \"floor exercise\", \"from\": 17514, \"to\": 17528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike the team competition on Tuesday, today's action will be gymnasts competing for individual glory, so they will not be rel