 exercise (Aug. 5) all still coming up.\", \"from\": 18652, \"to\": 18821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"separate individual finals\", \"from\": 18662, \"to\": 18688}, {\"ngram\": \"each event\", \"from\": 18693, \"to\": 18703}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 18710, \"to\": 18719}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 18721, \"to\": 18725}, {\"ngram\": \"uneven bars\", \"from\": 18730, \"to\": 18741}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 18743, \"to\": 18747}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance beam\", \"from\": 18756, \"to\": 18772}, {\"ngram\": \"floor exercise\", \"from\": 18777, \"to\": 18791}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 18793, \"to\": 18797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those upcoming finals can reward specialists who are really talented at a single event, whereas today is all about who is strong across multiple events.\", \"from\": 18823, \"to\": 18975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those upcoming finals\", \"from\": 18823, \"to\": 18844}, {\"ngram\": \"specialists\", \"from\": 18856, \"to\": 18867}, {\"ngram\": \"a single event\", \"from\": 18895, \"to\": 18909}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 18919, \"to\": 18924}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple events\", \"from\": 18959, \"to\": 18974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles did not attempt one of her most breathtaking signature moves, the Biles II, during the team competition on Tuesday, but she will go for it during the vault to start today's all-around final, NBC analyst Laurie Hernandez confirmed during the competition.\", \"from\": 18977, \"to\": 19243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19181, \"end\": 19184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.7735450018907348, \"rank\": 0.28223486119874863, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 19193, \"end\": 19209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"te